reference/

# macOS auto-saved screenshots (never commit)
Screenshot *.png
Screenshot *.jpg
Screenshot *.jpeg

# macOS Finder duplicate of theseus-codex (e.g. "theseus-codex 2", " 3")
theseus-codex [0-9]*/
